== Taglines ==
* Roads closed. Schools shut. Rules were made to be frozen!
* No School. No Rules. No Problem.

== Trivia ==
This is the first of two films to star both Josh Peck and Zena Gray, the other being [[Max_Keeble%27s_Big_Move|Max Keeble's Big Move]] made in 2001.

